1. e4 d6 (1... e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 (3. Bc4) (3. Bb5) (3. d4) 3... Nf6 4. Bc4?! { Italian Variation. } (4. d4) (4. Bb5) 4... Nxe4! 5. Bxf7+! (5. Nxe4 d5 6. Bd3 dxe4 7. Bxe4 Bd6) 5... Kxf7 6. Nxe4 d5 7. Neg5+ Kg8 8. d3 h6 9. Nh3 Bg4) 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 g6 4. Bc4 (4. f3 c6 5. Be3 Bg7 6. Qd2 O-O 7. O-O-O { PLAN 1. }) (4. Nf3 Bg7 5. Be2 (5. Bd3 O-O 6. Be3) 5... O-O 6. O-O { PLAN 2. }) 4... Bg7 5. b3? { - White is inconsistent, develops both sides, - Fianchetto makes no sense, because Bb2's view is blocked. - too slow - allows Nxe4. } 5... Nxe4! 6. Nxe4 (6. Bxf7+ Kxf7 7. Nxe4 Rf8 { Artificial castling. }) 6... d5 7. Bxd5 (7. Qf3) 7... Qxd5 8. Nc3 Qxd4?! (8... Qxg2 9. Qf3 Qxf3 10. Nxf3 Nc6) 9. Bb2 (9. Qxd4 Bxd4 10. Nb5 Bxa1! (10... Bb6?) 11. Nxc7+ Kd7 12. Nxa8 b6 13. Bf4 Na6 (13... e5 14. Be3 Bb7)) 9... O-O 10. Qxd4 Bxd4 11. O-O-O Nc6 (11... Bxf2!? 12. Nd5) 12. Nf3 Bxf2 13. Nd5 Bb6 14. Rhe1 Be6! (14... Re8?? 15. Nf6+) (14... e6? 15. Nf6+ Kg7 16. Nd7+ Kg8 17. Nxf8) (14... Bc5?! 15. Nxc7 Rb8) (14... Bg4 15. Rxe7 Nxe7?? 16. Nxe7#) 15. Nf4 Bg4 16. Rd3 Rfd8 17. Rc3 Rd7? (17... Ba5!) 18. Rxc6 bxc6 19. Ne5 Be3+! (19... Rd1+ 20. Rxd1 Be3+ 21. Rd2 Rd8 22. Nfd3 Bxd2+ 23. Kxd2 { Rook for 2 knights not great }) 20. Kb1 Rd1+ (20... Bxf4! 21. Nxg4 h5 22. Ne5 Bxe5 23. Bxe5 Rad8) 21. Rxd1 Bxd1 22. Nfd3 c5 23. c3 Rd8 24. Ne1 Be2 25. Kc2 Rd2+ 26. Kc1 Rd5+ 27. Kc2 Rxe5 28. c4 Bd4 29. Bc1 Bd3+?? 30. Nxd3 Re2+ 31. Kd1 Rxg2 32. h3 Rxa2 33. Ke1 Ra1 34. Kd2 Ra2+ 35. Ke1 Rh2 36. Nf4 e5 37. Nd5 Rxh3 38. Nxc7 Rxb3 39. Nd5 a5 40. Bd2 Rb1+ 41. Ke2 a4 42. Bc3 Bxc3 43. Nxc3 Rb2+ 44. Kf3 Rb3 45. Ke2 Rxc3 46. Kd2 Rxc4 47. Kd1 a3 48. Kd2 a2 49. Kd3 Rb4 50. Kc2 a1=Q 51. Kd2 Qa3 52. Kd1 Rb2 53. Kc1 Qa1# { 0-1 Black wins. } 0-1


