1. c4 d6?! (1... Nf6 2. Nc3 g6 3. g3 Bg7 4. Bg2 O-O 5. e3 c5 6. d4 cxd4 7. exd4 Qc7 8. b3 d5! 9. Nxd5 Nxd5 10. Bxd5 Nc6 11. Be3 Rd8 12. Ne2 Bg4 13. O-O e6) 2. g3 Nf6 3. Bg2 g6 4. d4 Bg7 5. Nc3 Nbd7?! (5... O-O! { "First thing, hide the king!!" }) 6. e3 c6 (6... O-O! { "First thing, hide the king!!" }) 7. Nge2 O-O 8. O-O Qc7 9. b3 e5 10. Bb2 b6? { Weakens your position too much, } (10... exd4! 11. exd4 Re8 12. Re1 (12. Qd2 Nf8 13. d5 (13. c5 d5) 13... c5) 12... Nf8) 11. d5 (11. Nb5!) 11... cxd5? (11... c5!) 12. Nb5? (12. Nxd5 Nxd5 13. Qxd5 Rb8 14. Rfd1 Bb7 15. Qxd6 Qxd6 16. Rxd6 Bxg2 17. Kxg2) 12... Qb8 13. Bxd5 Nxd5 14. Qxd5 Bb7 15. Qxd6 Qxd6 (15... Qe8) (15... Qc8 16. Qc7) 16. Nxd6 Bf3 17. Nc3 Nc5 18. Ba3 e4 19. Rac1 Nd3 20. Rc2 f5 21. Nd5 Rfd8 22. Nc7 Rab8 23. Ne6 Rd7 24. Rd2 Bc3 25. Rc2 Bb4 26. Bxb4 Nxb4 27. Rd2 Nd3! (27... Nxa2 28. Nxf5 (28. Nxe4 Rxd2 29. Nxd2)) 28. Nb5 a6 (28... Nf4!! 29. gxf4 (29. Nxf4) (29. exf4 Rxd2) (29. Rxd7 Nh3#) 29... Rxd2) 29. Nbd4 Re8 30. Nxf3 Rxe6 31. Rfd1 Red6 32. Ne5 Rd8 33. Nxd3 Rxd3 (33... exd3) 34. Rxd3 exd3 (34... Rxd3 35. Rxd3 exd3) 35. f3 (35. Kf1) 35... Kf7 36. Kf2 Ke6 37. e4 fxe4 38. fxe4 Ke5 39. Ke3 d2 40. Rxd2 Rxd2 41. Kxd2 Kxe4 42. Kc3 a5 (42... g5 43. b4 g4 (43... a5 44. bxa5 bxa5 45. c5 Kd5) 44. c5 bxc5 45. bxc5 Kd5 46. Kb4) 43. a3 h5 44. b4 axb4+ 45. axb4 g5 46. b5 Ke5 47. c5 bxc5 48. b6 Kd6 49. b7 Kc7 50. b8=Q+ Kxb8 51. Kc4 Kc7 52. Kxc5 Kd7 53. Kd5 h4 54. g4 (54. gxh4 gxh4) 54... h3 55. Ke5 Ke7 56. Kf5 Kf7 57. Kxg5 Kg7 58. Kh4 Kh6 59. Kxh3 Kg5 60. Kg3 Kg6 61. h4 Kh6 62. Kf4 Kg6 63. h5+ Kh6 64. Kf5 Kg7 65. g5 Kh7 66. g6+ Kg7 67. h6+ Kh8 68. Kf6 Kg8 69. h7+ Kh8 70. g7+ Kxh7 { 1-0 White wins. } 1-0


